        <mxCell id="GIb7ujWcDjvPRv6p48lb-36" parent="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=2;fillWeight=2;hachureGap=8;fillColor=#990000;fillStyle=dots;sketch=1;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="106" x="196" y="1194" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="GIb7ujWcDjvPRv6p48lb-37" parent="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=2;fillWeight=2;hachureGap=8;fillColor=#990000;fillStyle=dots;sketch=1;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="106" x="69" y="1189" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="GIb7ujWcDjvPRv6p48lb-38" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=17;" value="技能顺序:&lt;div&gt;1.千机雷压:从现在开始到战斗结束,每隔3秒进行一次全场AOE,伤害大约300w(减伤护盾均有效,此时boss60%易伤)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.第二次&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;玄磁激振+4圈重叠承伤&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;3.炽灼炎轨:连续点名5次当前主T,形成残留火焰&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;4.单&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;玄磁激振&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5.电涌:点名8个远程,结束会有雷圈残留(同P1跑圈前),并且清空5条火焰残留.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6.boss周期性会有矩形平A(同P1),T会带平A靠边,其他人躲好平A矩形&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="380" x="382" y="1159" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="GIb7ujWcDjvPRv6p48lb-39" parent="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;textShadow=0;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="290" x="38" y="438" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
